Overwolf,is,a,service,that,allows,users,to,integrate,social,applications,such,as,Facebook,Twitter,and,IM,clients,into,video,and,mobile,games,The,Overwolf,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Overwolf,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,resizing,windows,retrieving,information,from,games,and,creating,files,from,games